The evidence with the title 'Ad credits Newt Gingrich with balancing the budget | politifact ' says Dec 28, 2011  ... A tv ad airing in Iowa in the final week before the caucuses calls Newt Gingrich a " principled conservative" who has "fought for us." Here's how: "Newt balanced the federal budget, reformed welfare, cut taxes and created 11 million new jobs," a man's voice says as photos of Gingrich flash on the screen. 
